videos.description: Jack Podlesny's kick goes wide as he misses a 36-yard field goal to give Georgia the lead early in the second quarter.

videos.description: Clemson recovers its own punt after the ball bounces off the shoelaces of a Georgia player on the recovery.

videos.headline: Clemson comes away with Georgia muffed punt

videos.description: Georgia's Christopher Smith comes up with the interception and jets 74 yards down the field to reach the end zone and give the Bulldogs a 7-0 lead over Clemson.
videos.headline: Georgia scores on 74-yard pick-6

videos.description: Georgia brings the pressure all game against Clemson as it racks up seven sacks in a 10-3 win over the Tigers.
